{"tid":41436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄國退休阿伯願代坐監  每日收$374","createTime":"2016-12-16T01:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T01:50:42.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bae866f1df0ec3b79444d7ded64d06cbd2e2cff3","tid":41436,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161216&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56053734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161216%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56053734&d=hq1Tv1DQFqCq6TPm3S9dwgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=28a37fbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161216%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56053734&h=c86dfc8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161216&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56053734</a><br />\n俄羅斯一名退休男子，在國內最多人瀏覽的招聘網站刊登廣告，願意受薪代坐監，不過廣告迅速被下架。<br />\n該名頭髮灰白的退休老翁，在網站Avito.ru刊登廣告，表示「可代坐監最長4年，亦可代罪及代給證供」。不過他表明並非所有案件都接，涉及暴力及太瑣碎的案件不接，境外案件也非其服務範圍。<br />\n那麼他收取多少酬勞？廣告說：「關於酬金，坐監一天收3,000盧布(約374港元)」。不過，廣告上載不久便被網站刪掉。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/581Y6d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F581Y6d8.jpg&h=99845396&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}